payload.sql:
SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),
                     pg_get_expr(d.adbin, d.adrelid), a.attnotnull, a.atttypid, a.atttypmod
                FROM pg_attribute a LEFT JOIN pg_attrdef d
                  ON a.attrelid = d.adrelid AND a.attnum = d.adnum
               WHERE a.attrelid = '"spree_pages"'::regclass
                 AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
               ORDER BY a.attnum
payload.name: SCHEMA

payload.sql: SELECT  "spree_pages".* FROM "spree_pages" WHERE "spree_pages"."visible" = $1 AND "spree_pages"."slug" = $2  ORDER BY "spree_pages"."position" ASC LIMIT 1
payload.name: Spree::Page Load
